query:
SELECT 
  id,
  propertyId,
  buyer,
  county,
  state,
  originType,
  saleType,
  contractDate,
  transferDate,
  contractPrice,
  costBasis,
  downPayment,
  installmentAmount,
  installmentCount,
  balloonPayment,
  balloonPaymentDate,
  status,
  deedRecordedDate
FROM contracts
ORDER BY id;
